00:22:29,190 --> 00:22:30,023
- [Eli] Thank you.

544
00:22:30,023 --> 00:22:33,030
- [Yvonne] Yeah, that's a
great partnership story.

545
00:22:33,030 --> 00:22:35,100
Moving a little bit away
from the business side

546
00:22:35,100 --> 00:22:38,340
