549
00:22:43,320 --> 00:22:46,380
You often talk about
being a servant leader,

550
00:22:46,380 --> 00:22:48,570
one that aims to serve others.

551
00:22:48,570 --> 00:22:51,981
You talk openly about your
failures and vulnerabilities.

552
00:22:51,981 --> 00:22:54,390
How do you think sharing
some of those experiences

553
00:22:54,390 --> 00:22:57,120
have shaped you into the
leader you are today?

554
00:22:57,120 --> 00:22:58,370
- [Blake] Hmm, thank you.

555
00:22:59,460 --> 00:23:01,980
Well, I think when you hear
