really serve your customers,

561
00:23:18,570 --> 00:23:20,640
they need to be served from their managers

562
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:22,170
and I think that's really the job

563
00:23:22,170 --> 00:23:24,840
of a manager or an executive,

564
00:23:24,840 --> 00:23:27,240
