are not gonna be reprimanded.

576
00:24:03,210 --> 00:24:04,590
If anything, they're gonna be celebrated

577
00:24:04,590 --> 00:24:07,290
because what did we
learn from that failure?

578
00:24:07,290 --> 00:24:09,743
And I think that's a really
important part of leadership.

579
00:24:12,420 --> 00:24:13,290
- [Eli] I love hearing that.

580
00:24:13,290 --> 00:24:15,390
And I think one other thing we hear

581
