the luckier you get.

597
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:57,800
But I also think that,
sometimes just an idea,

598
00:24:57,990 --> 00:24:59,640
I mean, how do we have an idea?

599
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:02,940
Start there, like, I'm
sitting on a farm in Argentina

