had this kind of belief

798
00:33:08,760 --> 00:33:12,630
that to found a successful company,

799
00:33:12,630 --> 00:33:15,990
it really has to come from
a passion, from a need,

800
00:33:15,990 --> 00:33:18,120
from something that
you've seen in the world

801
00:33:18,120 --> 00:33:20,760
that you're frustrated with
or you don't agree with

802
00:33:20,760 --> 00:33:24,450
or there's a product you wish
you had but you can't buy.

803
00:33:24,450 --> 00:33:25,650
I really believe

804
00:33:25,650 --> 00:33:28,140
that that's where the
great businesses come from.

805
00:33:28,140 --> 00:33:32,310
I think it's very dangerous
to come get your MBA,

806
00:33:32,310 --> 00:33:33,420
