808
00:33:34,950 --> 00:33:36,540
I'm just gonna go start a business,

809
00:33:36,540 --> 00:33:38,070
without the passion behind it,

810
00:33:38,070 --> 00:33:39,840
just 'cause you think
you're gonna make money.

811
00:33:39,840 --> 00:33:42,660
I've seen most of those
businesses fail, to be honest.

812
00:33:42,660 --> 00:33:46,080
And so, if you make
making money the reason

813
00:33:46,080 --> 00:33:47,700
