841
00:34:56,970 --> 00:34:58,190
And I'm not saying making money

842
00:34:58,190 --> 00:35:00,000
is the only reason that we work,

843
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:01,920
but it is one of the reasons.

844
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:05,580
And so, what I tell people
is like instead of going out

845
00:35:05,580 --> 00:35:08,310
